## Lifecycle

```
1. Literature review → hypothesis portfolio (first H per Purpose)
2. One notebook per Purpose; one or more H rounds tested inside it
3. At each H round: bug_review → robustness battery → experiment-review → per-H verdict → append per-H row to results.parquet
4. If a derived H serves the same Purpose: continue with the next H round inside the SAME notebook
5. If the next investigation reflects a new Purpose: open the next notebook
6. Before completion: pass robustness battery (per H whose verdict is supported) and research-quality checklist
```

Detailed protocols live in the `quant-research` plugin's `references/` directory.
